51
00:02:57,647 --> 00:02:59,647
(and now I use this multiplication symbol right now)

52
00:02:59,642 --> 00:03:03,462
what do I have to multiply that by in order to get one?

53
00:03:03,461 --> 00:03:05,971
I just have to multiply it by the inverse of this

54
00:03:05,969 --> 00:03:08,139
the multiplicative inverse of this

55
